<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v1" title="Q30_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una ficha se registra la siguiente información sobre la venta de completos que organizan Carla y Tomás:<br />
    - Costo total de los ingredientes: $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
    - Aporte de Carla: $<m:math><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
    - Aporte de Tomás: el resto del costo.<br />
    - Cantidad de completos preparados: <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> completos.<br />
    - Precio de venta de cada completo: $<m:math><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
    <p>Deciden vender todos los completos y repartirse el dinero obtenido de forma proporcional a lo que cada uno aportó en la compra de los ingredientes. ¿Cuánto dinero recibirá Carla después de vender todos los completos?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">$18 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Carla aporta $18 000, pero no recibe solo su aporte inicial. El dinero total obtenido por la venta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como Carla aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del costo, debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no $18 000.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">$72 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Tomás aporta el resto del costo, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Carla aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del total. Al vender <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, Carla recibe <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">$60 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. $60 000 corresponde a la mitad de $120 000, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el reparto no es en partes iguales, sino proporcional a los aportes. Carla aportó $18 000 de $30 000, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no $60 000.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">$48 000<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Tomás aportó el resto del costo: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Eso equivale a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del costo total. Por eso <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> es lo que recibe Tomás. Carla recibe la parte restante: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>48&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular cuánto aportó Tomás</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total de los ingredientes es $30 000 y Carla aportó $18 000.</p>
            <p>Entonces, Tomás aportó el resto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Tomás aportó $12 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el dinero total obtenido por la venta</strong></p>
            <p>Se prepararon 80 completos y cada uno se vende a $1 500.</p>
            <p>Entonces, el dinero total recaudado es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Se obtienen $120 000 en total.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Determinar la proporción que aportó Carla</strong></p>
            <p>Carla aportó $18 000 de un total de $30 000.</p>
            <p>Su proporción es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>18&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Carla aportó <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del costo total.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular cuánto recibe Carla</strong></p>
            <p>Como el reparto es proporcional a lo aportado, Carla recibe <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de $120 000.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>120&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Carla recibe $72 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>: $72 000.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>